  <Placemark>
	<name>Southeast</name>
	<description>The Atlanta Beltline Northeast Trail will extend for 2.9 miles from Peachtree Creek just north of I-85 and continues south to Monroe Drive at Piedmont Park. It passes Ansley Golf Club and the Ansley Mall shopping center and extends along the eastern edge of Piedmont Park.</description>
