  <Placemark>
	<name>Northside</name>
	<description>The Atlanta Beltline Northside Trail winds for 2.9 miles from I-75 through Tanyard Creek Park to Peachtree Creek, treating visitors to one of the most secluded and picturesque stretches of the Atlanta Beltline.</description>
