	<name>Westside</name>
	<description>Winding through some of Atlanta’s oldest and most historic neighborhoods, the Atlanta Beltline Westside Trail is convenient to MARTA and buzzing with art displays and community pride. The trail extends 3.2 miles from I-20 to W Marietta Street.</description>
